---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="School Leadership Portfolio — Dr. Hamidah | 4 Schools, 4,750+ Students"
  description="Detailed portfolio of Dr. Hamidah's headteacher career across 4 Malaysian schools. From 250-student rural school to 1,700-student High-Performance School. Data-driven results."
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-900 to-navy-800 text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-gold-400 font-medium text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Leadership Portfolio</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">4 Schools. 12 Years. Consistent Results.</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-navy-200 max-w-2xl">Every school she led improved. Every community she built grew stronger. Here's the evidence.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Overview Stats -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-white border-b border-navy-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 gap-6 text-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-900 font-serif">12</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-navy-500 mt-1">Years as Headteacher</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-900 font-serif">4</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-navy-500 mt-1">Schools Led</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-900 font-serif">4,750+</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-navy-500 mt-1">Total Students Served</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-900 font-serif">396</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-navy-500 mt-1">Total Staff Managed</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-900 font-serif">9</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-navy-500 mt-1">Major Awards Won</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Schools Timeline -->
  <div class="relative">
    <!-- Timeline connector line — visible on desktop -->
    <div class="hidden md:block absolute left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-gold-400 via-navy-300 to-navy-200 -translate-x-0.5" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <!-- School 1: SK Kubang Kerian 3 — gold accent -->
    <section class="relative py-16 bg-white" id="sk-kubang-kerian-3">
      <!-- Timeline dot -->
      <div class="hidden md:flex absolute left-1/2 top-16 -translate-x-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gold-500 text-navy-900 text-xs font-bold items-center justify-center ring-4 ring-white shadow-sm z-10" aria-hidden="true">4th</div>
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="md:pl-8 border-l-4 border-l-gold-500 bg-gradient-to-r from-gold-50/40 to-transparent rounded-r-xl md:rounded-r-none pl-6 py-2">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="bg-gold-500 text-navy-900 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Current</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-navy-400">2024 – Present</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">SK Kubang Kerian 3</h2>
          <p class="text-navy-500 mb-6">Sekolah Berprestasi Tinggi (High-Performance School) · Kota Bharu, Kelantan</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8 mt-6">
          <div class="bg-navy-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900">1,700</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-navy-500">Students</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-navy-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900">131</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-navy-500">Teaching & Support Staff</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-navy-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900">SBT</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-navy-500">High-Performance Status</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="prose max-w-none text-navy-700">
          <p>SK Kubang Kerian 3 holds the prestigious Sekolah Berprestasi Tinggi (SBT) designation — one of the highest recognitions in Malaysian public education, awarded to schools demonstrating consistent academic excellence and strong leadership.</p>
          <p>As headteacher of one of Kelantan's largest primary schools, Dr. Hamidah manages an operation comparable to a mid-sized organisation: 131 staff across academic and support functions, serving 1,700 students from diverse backgrounds.</p>
        </div>

        <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900 mt-8 mb-3">Key Focus Areas</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-navy-700">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-sage-500 mt-0.5">✓</span> Maintaining High-Performance School standards across all KPIs</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-sage-500 mt-0.5">✓</span> Managing large-scale operations: budgeting, staffing, facilities</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-sage-500 mt-0.5">✓</span> Stakeholder management with parents, community, and district education office</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-sage-500 mt-0.5">✓</span> Awarded Excellent Service Award 2025</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Divider -->
    <div class="border-t border-navy-100" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <!-- School 2: SK Datu' Hashim — navy accent -->
    <section class="relative py-16 bg-white" id="sk-datu-hashim">
      <div class="hidden md:flex absolute left-1/2 top-16 -translate-x-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-navy-500 text-white text-xs font-bold items-center justify-center ring-4 ring-white shadow-sm z-10" aria-hidden="true">3rd</div>
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="md:pl-8 border-l-4 border-l-navy-400 pl-6 py-2">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="text-sm text-navy-400">2018 – 2024 (6 years)</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">SK Datu' Hashim</h2>
          <p class="text-navy-500 mb-6">Kota Bharu, Kelantan</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8 mt-6">
          <div class="bg-navy-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900">1,400</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-navy-500">Students</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-navy-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900">115</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-navy-500">Staff</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-navy-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900">6</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-navy-500">Years</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="prose max-w-none text-navy-700">
          <p>Dr. Hamidah's longest posting — six years of sustained impact. SK Datu' Hashim became her proving ground for digital transformation in education, a theme she would later explore in her PhD research.</p>
        </div>

        <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900 mt-8 mb-3">Key Achievements</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-navy-700">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-gold-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true"><svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9H4.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H6"/><path d="M18 9h1.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0-5H18"/><path d="M4 22h16"/><path d="M10 14.66V17c0 .55-.47.98-.97 1.21C7.85 18.75 7 20 7 22"/><path d="M14 14.66V17c0 .55.47.98.97 1.21C16.15 18.75 17 20 17 22"/><path d="M18 2H6v7a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V2Z"/></svg></span>
            <span><strong>DUTA Award 2021</strong> — State-level recognition for digital technology utilisation in education</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-gold-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true"><svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9H4.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H6"/><path d="M18 9h1.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0-5H18"/><path d="M4 22h16"/><path d="M10 14.66V17c0 .55-.47.98-.97 1.21C7.85 18.75 7 20 7 22"/><path d="M14 14.66V17c0 .55.47.98.97 1.21C16.15 18.75 17 20 17 22"/><path d="M18 2H6v7a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V2Z"/></svg></span>
            <span><strong>DUTA Award 2022</strong> — Won for the second consecutive year, demonstrating sustained digital innovation</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-sage-500 mt-0.5">✓</span> Implemented school-wide digital literacy programmes</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-sage-500 mt-0.5">✓</span> Led school through COVID-19 pandemic — pivoted to online learning while maintaining educational quality</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-sage-500 mt-0.5">✓</span> Awarded Excellent Service Award 2018</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Divider -->
    <div class="border-t border-navy-100" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <!-- School 3: SK Islah — sage accent (growth) -->
    <section class="relative py-16 bg-white" id="sk-islah">
      <div class="hidden md:flex absolute left-1/2 top-16 -translate-x-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-sage-500 text-white text-xs font-bold items-center justify-center ring-4 ring-white shadow-sm z-10" aria-hidden="true">2nd</div>
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="md:pl-8 border-l-4 border-l-sage-500 bg-gradient-to-r from-sage-50/40 to-transparent rounded-r-xl md:rounded-r-none pl-6 py-2">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="bg-sage-100 text-sage-700 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Best Academic Results</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-navy-400">2016 – 2018 (2 years)</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">SK Islah</h2>
          <p class="text-navy-500 mb-6">Kota Bharu, Kelantan</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8 mt-6">
          <div class="bg-navy-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900">1,400</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-navy-500">Students</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-navy-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900">115</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-navy-500">Staff</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-sage-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center border-2 border-sage-200">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-sage-700">300%</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-sage-600">UPSR Improvement</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="prose max-w-none text-navy-700">
          <p>SK Islah represents the most dramatic academic turnaround in Dr. Hamidah's career. In just two years, she quadrupled the number of students achieving straight As in the national UPSR examination.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Data visualization -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-navy-50 to-sage-50 rounded-xl p-6 mt-8">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-4">UPSR Straight-A Students (6As)</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div>
              <div class="flex justify-between text-sm mb-1"><span class="text-navy-700">2016 (Year 1)</span><span class="font-bold text-navy-900">3 students</span></div>
              <div class="h-4 bg-navy-200 rounded-full"><div class="h-4 bg-navy-600 rounded-full" style="width: 25%"></div></div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="flex justify-between text-sm mb-1"><span class="text-navy-700">2017 (Year 2)</span><span class="font-bold text-navy-900">7 students</span></div>
              <div class="h-4 bg-navy-200 rounded-full"><div class="h-4 bg-sage-500 rounded-full" style="width: 58%"></div></div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="flex justify-between text-sm mb-1"><span class="text-navy-700">2018 (Year 3)</span><span class="font-bold text-sage-700">12 students</span></div>
              <div class="h-4 bg-navy-200 rounded-full"><div class="h-4 bg-gold-500 rounded-full" style="width: 100%"></div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900 mt-8 mb-3">Key Achievements</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-navy-700">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-gold-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true"><svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9H4.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H6"/><path d="M18 9h1.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0-5H18"/><path d="M4 22h16"/><path d="M10 14.66V17c0 .55-.47.98-.97 1.21C7.85 18.75 7 20 7 22"/><path d="M14 14.66V17c0 .55.47.98.97 1.21C16.15 18.75 17 20 17 22"/><path d="M18 2H6v7a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V2Z"/></svg></span>
            <span><strong>STEM Principal Award 2018</strong> — State-level recognition for STEM integration</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-sage-500 mt-0.5">✓</span> 300% increase in UPSR straight-A achievers (3 → 12 students)</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-sage-500 mt-0.5">✓</span> Introduced STEM-focused programmes across all year levels</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-sage-500 mt-0.5">✓</span> Restructured academic support systems and teacher mentoring</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Divider -->
    <div class="border-t border-navy-100" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <!-- School 4: SK Temalir — navy accent -->
    <section class="relative py-16 bg-white" id="sk-temalir">
      <div class="hidden md:flex absolute left-1/2 top-16 -translate-x-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-navy-400 text-white text-xs font-bold items-center justify-center ring-4 ring-white shadow-sm z-10" aria-hidden="true">1st</div>
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="md:pl-8 border-l-4 border-l-navy-400 pl-6 py-2">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="bg-gold-100 text-gold-700 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">National Award Winner</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-navy-400">2014 – 2016 (2 years)</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">SK Temalir</h2>
          <p class="text-navy-500 mb-6">Kuala Krai, Kelantan (Rural)</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8 mt-6">
          <div class="bg-navy-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900">250</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-navy-500">Students</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-navy-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900">35</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-navy-500">Staff</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gold-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center border-2 border-gold-200">
            <span class="text-gold-600 inline-flex justify-center" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9H4.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H6"/><path d="M18 9h1.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0-5H18"/><path d="M4 22h16"/><path d="M10 14.66V17c0 .55-.47.98-.97 1.21C7.85 18.75 7 20 7 22"/><path d="M14 14.66V17c0 .55.47.98.97 1.21C16.15 18.75 17 20 17 22"/><path d="M18 2H6v7a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V2Z"/></svg>
            </span>
            <p class="text-xs text-gold-600">National Award</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="prose max-w-none text-navy-700">
          <p>Dr. Hamidah's first headteacher posting was in rural Kuala Krai — a small school far from the resources of the city. Rather than seeing this as a limitation, she turned it into an opportunity, building exceptional parent-community engagement that earned national recognition.</p>
        </div>

        <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900 mt-8 mb-3">Key Achievements</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-navy-700">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-gold-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true"><svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9H4.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H6"/><path d="M18 9h1.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0-5H18"/><path d="M4 22h16"/><path d="M10 14.66V17c0 .55-.47.98-.97 1.21C7.85 18.75 7 20 7 22"/><path d="M14 14.66V17c0 .55.47.98.97 1.21C16.15 18.75 17 20 17 22"/><path d="M18 2H6v7a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V2Z"/></svg></span>
            <span><strong>National-Level PIBG Excellence Award 2016</strong> — Recognised for outstanding parent-teacher-community collaboration</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-gold-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true"><svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9H4.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H6"/><path d="M18 9h1.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0-5H18"/><path d="M4 22h16"/><path d="M10 14.66V17c0 .55-.47.98-.97 1.21C7.85 18.75 7 20 7 22"/><path d="M14 14.66V17c0 .55.47.98.97 1.21C16.15 18.75 17 20 17 22"/><path d="M18 2H6v7a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V2Z"/></svg></span>
            <span><strong>State-Level Best Practices Award 2016</strong> — For parent and community involvement</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-sage-500 mt-0.5">✓</span> Transformed a rural school into a community hub</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-sage-500 mt-0.5">✓</span> Proved that school size doesn't determine school excellence</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-navy-900 text-white text-center">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mb-4">This Track Record Speaks for Itself</h2>
      <p class="text-navy-200 mb-8">Available for education leadership roles from March 2026. Let's talk about how 30 years of experience can benefit your institution.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-gold-500 hover:bg-gold-600 text-navy-900 font-bold rounded-lg transition-[background-color,box-shadow] duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold-500 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-gold-500/25">
          Get in Touch →
        </a>
        <a href="/research" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 border-2 border-navy-400 hover:border-white text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-[border-color] duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold-500 focus-visible:ring-offset-2">
          View Research
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
